Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.57,0:00:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... I wish there was a\Ngreat scoop somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.46,0:00:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hazama Residence
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.13,0:00:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.56,0:00:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.81,0:00:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.18,0:00:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. The old lady didn't want anyone\Nto know about this mirror...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.79,0:00:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and once we put it up in\NThursday's auction, we'll be rich!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.70,0:00:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope we get a good price.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.57,0:00:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We will.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.91,0:00:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.71,0:00:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You got the appraisal?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.35,0:00:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Right here.\NHurry up and drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.22,0:00:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.29,0:00:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Thieves...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.48,0:01:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my scoop!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.22,0:01:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mystical Princess Rosa's Mirror
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.51,0:01:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,My, it's such a finely crafted mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.32,0:01:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It was made in the 17th century\Nfor Princess Rosa of Reyche.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.77,0:01:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder...\Nit's such a magnificent mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.98,0:01:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is, last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.58,0:01:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the mirror was stolen\Nalong with its appraisal form.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.29,0:01:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a lovely legend regarding\Nthe princess who owned this mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.73,0:01:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Antique collectors around the\Nworld are anxious to possess it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.94,0:01:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If the word of its theft gets out...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.82,0:02:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I fear the collectors will do\Nanything to get their hands on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.73,0:02:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I merely want to live out my\Nlife in peace with my mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.94,0:02:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we can't notify\Nthe police either, can we...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.62,0:02:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No, all I can do is pray that it's\Nreturned to me without a scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.90,0:02:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.47,0:02:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us pray. I'm sure our\Nprayers will be answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.82,0:02:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And does she have any suspects?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.29,0:02:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the mirror could have only been\Nstolen by people in Mrs. Hazama's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.54,0:02:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,She knows those two wanted it\Nand has no doubt they stole it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.48,0:02:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,She says they visited her the\Nother evening and after they left...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,she noticed the mirror was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.26,0:02:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It was there when they arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.87,0:02:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll need to find out where they've\Nhidden it before you can get it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.25,0:03:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what I have to do Seira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.75,0:03:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.36,0:03:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's done!\NIt's all done!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.57,0:03:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Good Morning Miss Haneoka!\NBeautiful morning, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.14,0:03:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good morning Sawatari.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.45,0:03:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's the latest school newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.69,0:03:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, the feature story is my scoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.06,0:03:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirror stolen from estate...\NSt. Tail is the thief?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.51,0:03:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Haneoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.28,0:03:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Great, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.39,0:03:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how I'll\Nstrike a blow against St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got more secret\Ninformation on this case, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.28,0:03:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.82,0:03:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.99,0:03:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, monkey boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you calling a monkey?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.03,0:04:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail would never do\Nanything like this and you know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.81,0:04:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have any proof,\Nso don't print lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.09,0:04:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate,\Nyou'd better rewrite your story.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Th... they're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.53,0:04:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You wrote it without any proof...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.37,0:04:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,so you're the one who's going to\Nlook real bad in the end you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.61,0:04:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is she so upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.99,0:04:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me tell you something...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.86,0:04:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,we reporters stake\Nour lives on our stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.70,0:04:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The universe could explode,\Nbut we'd never rewrite our story!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.11,0:04:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He's hopeless.\NI guess I have no other choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.56,0:04:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.00,0:04:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,"My target is Princess Rosa's mirror...?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.40,0:04:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A... a scoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.64,0:04:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.25,0:04:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.42,0:05:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,A note from St. Tail is a great scoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.12,0:05:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to go rewrite my story!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.60,0:05:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me ladies! Adieu! Adios!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.17,0:05:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What was all that\Nabout never rewriting a story?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.28,0:05:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But it worked out well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Now he won't write about\Nthe mirror belonging to Mrs. Hazama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.26,0:05:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he knows more about the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.57,0:05:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Journalism Club
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd Sawatari go off to anyway?\NHe's not here or in the classroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.73,0:05:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always been interested in journalism,\Neven when I was younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.31,0:05:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? You too, Miss Haneoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.31,0:05:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.51,0:05:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawatari and Haneoka...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.79,0:05:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know you were\Ninterested in making the school paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.70,0:05:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Your constant enthusiasm\Nmust have rubbed off on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.81,0:06:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Look around for as long as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls are always welcome here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.28,0:06:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.89,0:06:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Why am I hiding for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.79,0:06:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, is this your camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you take this photo\Nwith this camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.51,0:06:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a lot more! Want to see?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.25,0:06:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.76,0:06:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You've even taken pictures of stars?\NThey're beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.01,0:06:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'd be\Nintruding if I go in now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.61,0:06:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But what I'm doing is eavesdropping...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.32,0:06:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I've put on a good act\Npretending to be interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.79,0:06:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Now all I have to\Ndo is get the information.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, about that mirror...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Haneoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.75,0:06:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:06:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.15,0:06:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.09,0:07:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Every girl who's come to me was\Nonly interested in my good looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.94,0:07:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the first one who\Nshowed an interest in my work!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.38,0:07:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.58,0:07:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.59,0:07:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Haneoka, if it's alright, would you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.53,0:07:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr.! Why is he here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.31,0:07:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Monkey boy, I want to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.31,0:07:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.55,0:07:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I have nothing to say to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.89,0:07:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He couldn't be jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.23,0:07:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawatari, you know a lot more\Nabout that mirror, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.41,0:07:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I guess not...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.08,0:07:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Reporters never reveal their sources.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.42,0:07:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The world could end,\Nbut we'd never talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.60,0:07:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to hear more about it, too.\NIt must be a beautiful mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.61,0:07:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.11,0:08:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a story about a\Nprincess in the mirror's history.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.68,0:08:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And it sure is interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.26,0:08:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you said you'd never talk,\Nnot even if the world came to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.57,0:08:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright already.\NYou want to hear it too, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Party pooper.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.91,0:08:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The legend behind this mirror...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.15,0:08:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,is a love story about\NPrincess Rosa of Reyche.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.76,0:08:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A love story?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.12,0:08:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I did some research and\Nlearned that a long time ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Rosa fell in love with a\Nyoung mirror maker from her village.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.35,0:08:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She was sad because\Nshe knew their love could never be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.39,0:08:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Then one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.59,0:08:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,she asked him to make a mirror\Nthat would reflect her true self.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.70,0:08:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the figure in royal robes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And when the mirror was\Nfinished and brought to the castle...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.65,0:08:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The woman reflected on\Nit was not Princess Rosa...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.15,0:08:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,but a simple young maiden named Rosa,\Nher face filled with love.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.56,0:09:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The princess forsook her title...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.83,0:09:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and took only the mirror with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.50,0:09:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,She left the castle\Nto marry the mirror maker.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.47,0:09:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And they lived happily ever after.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.15,0:09:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It has been said that any\Nwoman possessing that mirror...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.22,0:09:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,will live in happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.89,0:09:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The real me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.83,0:09:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A mirror that will reflect\Nthe me that isn't St. Tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.55,0:09:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that's why antique\Ncollectors around the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.29,0:09:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,especially women,\Nall want that mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.96,0:09:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't even estimate\Nhow much it will sell for.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.04,0:09:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And why would\NSt. Tail want that mirror?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.41,0:09:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,As I suspected.\NIt's always about St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.09,0:09:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.26,0:09:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is top secret...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.33,0:09:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,the mirror is being put\Non the block at the city's auction.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.64,0:09:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.89,0:10:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.43,0:10:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.64,0:10:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.78,0:10:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.69,0:10:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving now Ruby.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.16,0:10:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Seira, I want to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.23,0:10:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you put a\Nstolen item up for auction?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.77,0:10:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.15,0:10:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But the thieves also\Ntook the appraisal slip with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.36,0:10:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.53,0:10:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of Ruby please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.44,0:11:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.08,0:11:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,May God bless and protect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.01,0:11:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This magnificent Evans violin...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.45,0:11:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,has been sold for\N20 million dollars to this gentleman.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.58,0:11:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you, don't get in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.65,0:12:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight's the\Nnight I capture St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.23,0:12:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave you important information.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.90,0:12:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The least you can do is\Nlet me photograph the auction.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.26,0:12:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The next item...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.23,0:12:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,is something we collectors have\Nbeen searching for for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.20,0:12:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And now we have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.47,0:12:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The famous Princess Rosa's Mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.53,0:12:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.87,0:12:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the famous\NPrincess Rosa's mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.84,0:12:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fabulous!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.29,0:12:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.13,0:12:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to the lights?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.10,0:12:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:13:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha...? A flower?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.18,0:13:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This flower is called...\NThe Princess Rosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.69,0:13:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Reyche's national flower!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.66,0:13:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They're lovely...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I get it!\NIt's part of the presentation!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.20,0:13:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.51,0:13:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The ceiling!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.92,0:13:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! That mirror was stolen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.90,0:13:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Who said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.47,0:13:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It couldn't be the Princess' ghost...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.61,0:13:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, everyone,\Nplease remain calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening.\NPlease forgive my intrusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.69,0:13:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?\NWhere's that voice coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.43,0:13:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'd been on the stage...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.90,0:13:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,she'd have been in my\Nblind spot and gotten away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.24,0:13:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I was right about staying right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.68,0:13:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two men stole that mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.22,0:13:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Stolen property... so you didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.56,0:14:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.87,0:14:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we're in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.88,0:14:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you've been discovered,\Nwhy don't you be good and return it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.99,0:14:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!\NWe worked hard to get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.97,0:14:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, here's my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to beat that St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.64,0:14:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.43,0:14:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Show Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.76,0:15:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.33,0:15:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,For you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.34,0:15:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.18,0:15:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.75,0:15:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.18,0:15:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.61,0:15:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A reflection of one's true image...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.29,0:16:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The lights are back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.16,0:16:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn! The mirror's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.10,0:16:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look on the stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.14,0:16:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.67,0:16:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The thieves?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.73,0:16:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"I have taken\NPrincess Rosa's mirror, St. Tail. "
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.77,0:16:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.00,0:16:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It was so bright,\NI couldn't take any pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.04,0:16:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What's gonna happen to my scoop?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.38,0:16:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It was never meant to\Nbe printed in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.69,0:16:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.70,0:16:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that back there I saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.69,0:17:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord, thank you for\Nreturning my mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.16,0:17:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,"St. Tail returns priceless mirror.\NMirror taken from auction block. "
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.23,0:17:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.50,0:17:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,My scoop made the front page again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.14,0:17:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He never gives up...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.58,0:17:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.62,0:17:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.06,0:17:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Your hair looks nice today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.36,0:17:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.93,0:17:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it does...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.50,0:17:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you at the auction last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.59,0:18:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.76,0:18:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he catch on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.00,0:18:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.58,0:18:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me! I'm St. Tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.96,0:18:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.37,0:18:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you asking me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.72,0:18:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,As if I'd answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.09,0:18:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.93,0:18:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, it's unscientific to see\Nsomeone else's reflection in a mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.18,0:18:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The lights blinded me for awhile...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.22,0:18:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe something happened to my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.63,0:19:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I must have been seeing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.47,0:19:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I was hallucinating, then why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.99,0:19:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why was it that I saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.39,0:19:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Haneoka?
